responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "C312E81B48A85DC37296ED86A7337791", "The league is collecting on some dues which this family owes, but I can\'t seem to get through to the fisherman\'s wife. She says the smugglers swept through here not long ago. Though, the poor wretches got their bruises, she says. This is the dreadful part of lending in the Skip, they really couldn\'t give you a harder time. You seem to be fine on you rown though, those riffraff bandits didn\'t even get a scratch on your armor.")
